NFL Post-Week 10 Bettor Misery Index: 

RIP @RamsNFL bettors, who collectively lost the most money in back-to-back weeks 😭 

Chiefs bettors got a bit of respite after a miserable season-to-date. Packers/Cowboys bettors continue to cash tickets (combined 17-2 ATS) 🤑

Cam Newton in/Chase Young out. Panthers bid up another 2pts 📈

Justified repricings?
